With space-saving layouts and rugged construction, these campers make camping simple, safe, and budget-friendly—so you can focus on having fun in the great outdoors.

 

Key Features of the Go Play 26BHSW

 

Camp-Ready

Built For Durability

Key Features of the Go Play 26BHSW

 

Camp-Ready

Built For Durability

Spacious, Functional Interiors

 

With an 8-foot-wide design and 6'9" ceilings, the Go Play provides more headroom and living space than many other conventional built travel trailers. Smart storage solutions and added features like coat and towel hooks, and a dedicated wastebasket space make every Go Play interior functional.

  • Hidden Pantry

Choose a Wildwood X-Lite travel trailer today for quality and value!

units.details:

  • Front Private Bedroom
  • Kitchen Pantry
  • Full Bath
  • 12' 12V Power Awning

Camping is made easy in this travel trailer with more sleeping space and lots of comforts! The kids or your guests will enjoy the double-size bunks in the back, along with the full bath close by for easy nighttime use. You'll have the front private bedroom with a king bed all to yourselves, and there are dual bedroom wardrobes to keep your space neat and clean. Everyone can meet in the combined kitchen and living room to relax on the super U-lounge with a removable table while the chef of your group makes breakfast on the two-burner cooktop. There is also a microwave oven for quick meals, plus a pantry and large under counter refrigerator for food storage!

 

The Forest River Wildwood FSX Limited Edition travel trailer is easy to tow and easy to love, so come take a look! You'll appreciate the aerodynamic front profile, diamond plate front rock guard, and seamless holding tanks. The 26" entry doors are easy to access. A dedicated cable TV hookup is located on the exterior, so you can settle in under the power awning and watch some TV.

This charming travel trailer is perfect for families or small groups. The front bedroom features a full bed, perfect for a restful night's sleep. Ample storage space ensures you stay organized and clutter-free. The booth dinette is a cozy spot for meals and conversation, while the kitchen area is equipped with a microwave, fridge, and overhead cabinets. Prepare delicious meals and snacks with ease.   • Theatre Seating
  • Booth Dinette

  • Dual Opposing Slides
  • Living Area Skylight
  • Spacious Full Bath
  • Front Private Bedroom
  • Oversized Panoramic Windows
